  "html": "<p class=\"\">I needed to backup thousands of photos from Cloudinary, and couldn't find an easy standalone tool to do so. So I built a little desktop app with Tauri. It handles batch downloads without eating all your RAM (vs an Electron app) and lets you resume if something goes wrong.</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p><figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Setup instructions for Cloudinary Backup tool requesting cloud name, API key, and API secret credentials to download photos.\" class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1755100480/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.54.28_AM.png\" alt=\"Setup instructions for Cloudinary Backup tool requesting cloud name, API key, and API secret credentials to download photos.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1755100480/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.54.28_AM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1755100480/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.54.28_AM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1755100480/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.54.28_AM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1755100480/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.54.28_AM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Setup instructions for Cloudinary Backup tool requesting cloud name, API key, and API secret credentials to download photos.\" style=\"background-color:#222222;background-image:url(&#x22;data:image/jpeg;base64,&#x22;);background-size:cover;background-position:center;--splay-rot:2.67deg;\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1750\" data-dimensions=\"2000×1750\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"><figcaption class=\"\">Setup instructions for Cloudinary Backup tool requesting cloud name, API key, and API secret credentials to download photos.</figcaption></figure><p class=\"\"></p>",
